<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BAaaS Landing Page</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A simple landing page for BAaaS."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <section id="hero" class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">BAaaS</p>
        <h1>Build your business backend faster.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          A simple landing page test for the BAaaS project. We will replace this
          text with the real offer, benefits, and call to action.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="button">Contact us</a>
          <a href="#features" class="link">See features</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="problem">
        <h2>The problem</h2>
        <p>
          Most small teams waste time setting up repetitive business systems
          instead of focusing on customers and growth.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="solution">
        <h2>The solution</h2>
        <p>
          BAaaS helps package common business processes into a simple, reusable
          service layer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="features">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <article>
            <h3>Fast setup</h3>
            <p>Launch quickly without overbuilding the first version.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Simple workflow</h3>
            <p>Keep the process understandable for non-technical users.</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Analytics-ready</h3>
            <p>Track which sections and pages visitors care about.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="pricing">
        <h2>Pricing</h2>
        <p>
          Pricing will be added later. For now, this section proves that
          analytics can track interest in pricing.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="faq">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <details>
          <summary>Is this the final design?</summary>
          <p>No. This is the first working version so we can test deployment.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Will we add Google Analytics?</summary>
          <p>Yes. After this page deploys successfully.</p>
        </details>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Interested? Email us or connect a form here later.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@example.com" class="button">Email us</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    color: #172033;
    background: #f6f7fb;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
  }

  main {
    width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e7ef;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #5263ff;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  p {
    max-width: 680px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #4d5668;
  }

  .lead {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 22px;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 0 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #172033;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .link {
    color: #172033;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  article {
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #e4e7ef;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: white;
  }

  details {
    max-width: 720px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e7ef;
  }

  summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    section {
      padding: 56px 0;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>